data.description: FANTASTIC ONE-STORY HOME IN A CORNER LOT!. This spacious open floor plan includes; four bedrooms, two full bath, kitchen with a large island breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and birch cabinetry with crown molding. Large covered patio back patio for relaxing and extended drive way for extra parking. Excellent LOCATION! , Easy access to BW-8, I-10, and HWY-90, Airports, medical center, schools, shopping and dinning center. Make your appointment today!
